Subject: [RFC PATCH v2 1/7] x86/hyperv: Allocate RMP table during boot
Date:   Mon, 13 Feb 2023 10:33:56 +0000
Message-Id: <20230213103402.1189285-2-jpiotrowski@linux.microsoft.com>
